high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife in front of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table with the coffee maker on it.
Use the knife to slice the potato next to the sponge.
Turn around to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the knife on a shelf.
Close the refrigerator door and return to the sliced potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left and walk to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave, cook it, then remove it.
Back up from the sink, look to the left, then back at the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooked potato in the sink.

high_descs: turn left, go to sink on the right
pick up knife from in front of sink on the left
turn around, go toward window, turn left to face table
slice potato to the left of green sponge
turn around, go to refrigerator
open refrigerator, place knife on top of tomato on second shelf, close refrigerator
turn left, go toward window
pick up potato slice from table to the left
turn around, go to microwave above sink
place potato slice on plate in microwave, close door, microwave potato slice, remove potato slice from microwave, close microwave door
look down to sink on the left
place potato slice in right side of the sink on the left
anns.task_desc: Place microwaved potato slice in left sink

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward, and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around, walk across the room, and then turn to the left to face the table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around face the end of the table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn left, walk across the room, and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice and remove it from the microwave.
Step to the left and look down to face the sink.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato slice and put it in the sink.
